This is an example of an ARM firmware project that can be used with or without the bootloader.


Pins used:
* PA2 - serial data out of ARM processor
* PA3 - serial data in to ARM processor


To use it without the bootloader, run:

rosmake
st-flash write build/firmware_out/firmware.bin 0x8000000
bin/stm32f3discovery_imu_driver --no-bootloader


To use it with the bootloader, run:

rosmake
st-flash write `rospack find arm_bootloader`/build/firmware_out/firmware.bin 0x8000000
bin/stm32f3discovery_imu_driver
